snippet.title: Auf Abwegen - Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore the beauty and dangers of nature in this narrative 2D mini-puzzle-platformer - a one-man project from Kindman.
Slip into the role of a red fox in its natural habitat - feed your family and survive the threats of the forest - and humans too!

Initially Free - Get it on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1036850/Auf_Abwegen/
Enjoy ;)
